# ML Models Directory

This directory will contain trained machine learning models:

- `legal_ner_model/` - Custom Named Entity Recognition model for legal entities
- `document_classifier/` - Document structure classification model
- `summarization_model/` - Fine-tuned summarization model (BART/T5)
- `rights_classifier/` - Constitutional rights violation classifier

Models are excluded from git due to large file sizes.

For model training, see:

- `notebooks/train_legal_ner.ipynb`
- `notebooks/train_document_classifier.ipynb`
- `notebooks/train_summarization_model.ipynb`
- `notebooks/train_rights_classifier.ipynb`
